  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain a glimpse of the present reality around you. Choose one of the following effects:</p><ul><li><p>You determine which way is North</p></li><li><p>You discern which plane of existence you are on</p></li><li><p>You determine the link between an object you touch and its significant counterpart. For example, if the object is a key, you learn what the key unlocks. If the lock is within 30 feet of you, you learn its exact location. Otherwise, you only learn a vague description of the lock's location, as as \"a treasure chest amongst a shipwreck\" or \"a sealed spell tome.\"</p></li><li><p>You gain a glimpse of who last wore a specific piece of jewelry or clothing, or who last wielded a particular weapon you touch. If the object had never been worn or wielded, then you see who created it instead.</p></li><li><p>You discern whether something is out of place with an object or part of a structure (such as a wall or door) that you can touch. If the object is under the effects of magic, or if it is hiding a secret of any kind, you sense that something is strange about it. You do not discern the particulars.</p></li></ul>",
